{"tid":1035603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有時真係唔係惡意針對...","createTime":"2019-02-24T16:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T10:43:55.000Z","uid":212800,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8a31e8ed459aff9ac7fa7164a9d41b020acc87","tid":1035603,"uid":212800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"當你諗住同大陸人理性同客觀咁討論一件事時，硬係有啲人會衝出嚟撩交嗌話我哋睇唔起佢哋呢啲大陸人，然後再講大陸而家有幾勁，有幾巴閉，同埋咩香港都係祖國嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到最後你又要同佢開火，但明明一開始嗰陣，你一字一句裏面根本都冇咁嘅意思...<br />\n<br />\n大佬你使唔使咁玻璃心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪之得全世界都知你玻璃心啦，小小事都起晒鋼，有時候真係唔好話人哋針對你哋，好多嘢都係你自己攞嚟"},{"pid":"dacf06b1139f8e369894bf66eaf190b672566649","tid":1035603,"uid":212800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6b8381cb7b115c43b72b429af62d7cf983982ae","tid":1035603,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"典型自卑轉自大"},{"pid":"3f134337837ff2b36a78a62cf1e851f4aff3db2c","tid":1035603,"uid":212800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6b8381cb7b115c43b72b429af62d7cf983982ae","tid":1035603,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"典型自卑轉自大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"同大陸人真係好難理性討論"},{"pid":"544722ed4d20b900a05830766f1020385d26f3dd","tid":1035603,"uid":212800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:16:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8756fecc4991fdcfe1663ebc816498eee83818fe","tid":1035603,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"對住啲野蠻人講道理<br />\n慳番啖氣啦<br />\n班生蕃根本未開發"},{"pid":"5c0d18bbad438084d797c3da9f7c164ec73e4635","tid":1035603,"uid":212800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8756fecc4991fdcfe1663ebc816498eee83818fe","tid":1035603,"uid":158888,"li